Key response data contains all the data needed to facilitate a exchange of session keys from the responseor.

Specific key exchange mechanisms should define their own key response data types.

Key response data is represented as keyresponsedata = { "#mandatory" : [ "mastertoken", "scheme", "keydata" ], "mastertoken" : mastertoken, "scheme" : "string", "keydata" : object } where:

  • mastertoken is the master token associated with the session keys
  • scheme is the key exchange scheme
  • keydata is the scheme-specific key data
